OL,3,CHMRC has 'failed to use new powers'
OL,4,Caround retail tax evasion, says
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FThe UK is failing to tackle tax
OL,8,Fevasion among retailers despite new
OL,9,Fgovernment powers, according to a new
OL,10,Freport by the UK's public spending
OL,11,Fwatchdog.
OL,13,FThe National Audit Office said the
OL,14,FGovernment "lacks an effective
OL,15,Fresponse" to illegal tax dodgers in
OL,16,Fthe sector, amid a sharp increase in
OL,17,Fthe problem in recent years.
