OL,3,CHMRC has 'failed to use new powers'
OL,4,Caround retail tax evasion, says
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FHM Revenue and Customs' (HMRC) most
OL,8,Frecent figures, from 2022-23, estimate
OL,9,Fthat #5.5 billion was lost due to tax
OL,10,Fevasion, 81% of it from small
OL,11,Fbusinesses, up from 66% in 2019-20.
OL,13,FBut the department currently "does not
OL,14,Fhave a specific strategy" to clamp
OL,15,Fdown on the issue, the NAO said.
OL,17,FOne particular issue is retailers that
OL,18,Fallow themselves to go insolvent then
OL,19,Fset up again under a new registration,
OL,20,Fso the same directors can carry on
OL,21,Ftrading.
