OL,3,CHMRC has 'failed to use new powers'
OL,4,Caround retail tax evasion, says
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FHMRC estimated the practice, known as
OL,8,Fphoenixism, accounted for 15% of its
OL,9,Ftax debt losses in 2022-23, equivalent
OL,10,Fto more than #500 million.
OL,12,FHowever, the Insolvency Service
OL,13,Fdisqualified only seven directors
OL,14,Fspecifically for phoenixism between
OL,15,F2018-19 and 2023-24, out of a total of
OL,16,F6,274 disqualified directors.
