OL,4,Caround retail tax evasion, says
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FMeanwhile, new powers to issue
OL,8,Fpenalties for businesses that falsely
OL,9,Fmanipulate the amount of money passing
OL,10,Fthrough their till ` known as
OL,11,Felectronic sales suppression ` came
OL,12,Finto force in 2022.
OL,14,FThe NAO said that HMRC has still not
OL,15,Fyet issued any civil penalties using
OL,16,Fthe powers, but that the department
OL,17,Ftold report writers that publicity
OL,18,Faround their existence has "had a
OL,19,Fdeterrent effect".
