OL,3,CHMRC has 'failed to use new powers'
OL,4,Caround retail tax evasion, says
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FGareth Davies, head of the NAO, said:
OL,8,F"Although tax evasion has been growing
OL,9,Famong small businesses, HMRC has so
OL,10,Ffar lacked an effective strategic
OL,11,Fresponse.
OL,13,F"Its assessment of risks has given too
OL,14,Flittle emphasis to widely used methods
OL,15,Fof evasion such as sales suppression
OL,16,Fand phoenixism. It has also failed to
OL,17,Fuse new powers to tackle tax evasion.
