OL,3,CHMRC has 'failed to use new powers'
OL,4,Caround retail tax evasion, says
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,F"Tackling tax evasion is not a
OL,8,Fstraightforward task. But real
OL,9,Fopportunities exist for HMRC to work
OL,10,Fmore systematically across government
OL,11,Fto reduce it. Tighter controls and
OL,12,Fmore compliance work could raise
OL,13,Fsignificant sums and improve value for
OL,14,Fmoney."
OL,16,FIt comes after Labour said during the
OL,17,Fgeneral election that it will crack
OL,18,Fdown on tax avoiders to pay for its
OL,19,Fcommitments on schools and the NHS.
