OL,7,FThe party said it will try to raise #5
OL,8,Fbillion a year by the end of the next
OL,9,FParliament by narrowing the "tax gap"
OL,10,F` the difference between the amount of
OL,11,Fmoney HMRC is owed and the amount it
OL,12,Factually receives.
OL,14,FElsewhere, the NAO added that
OL,15,Ffraudulent businesses setting up on
OL,16,FCompanies House, the UK's register of
OL,17,Fcompanies, is still an issue despite
OL,18,Fthe Government introducing tighter
OL,19,Frequirements in March.
