OL,7,FWhile new powers in March are supposed
OL,8,Fto allow officials to request evidence
OL,9,Fon company registrations, verify
OL,10,Fdirectors' identities and remove
OL,11,Finaccurate listings, some of the
OL,12,Fmeasures will still "not be fully
OL,13,Foperational until Companies House
OL,14,Fdevelops the necessary systems and
OL,15,Fcapability".
OL,17,FAn HMRC spokesperson said: "The UK has
OL,18,Fone of the lowest tax gaps reported in
OL,19,Fthe world, but the Government is
OL,20,Fcommitted to reducing it further.
