OL,7,F"While the vast majority of businesses
OL,8,Fpay the tax that's due, we will
OL,9,Fcontinue to use our civil and criminal
OL,10,Fpowers against the determined minority
OL,11,Fwho refuse to play by the rules. Such
OL,12,Faction helped us protect #41.8 billion
OL,13,Fin the last 12 months.
OL,15,F"We also work closely with partners
OL,16,Fincluding the Insolvency Service and
OL,17,FCompanies House to tackle evasion in
OL,18,Fretail and online services."
